Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: opkode.rateablediscussion
Version: 0.1a2
Summary: Allows plone.app.discussion comments to be rated.
Home-page: http://opkode.net
Author: JC Brand
Author-email: jc@opkode.com
License: GPL
Description: Introduction
        ============
        
        This package provides the ability for users to rate the comments in Plone. 
        They can do this by clicking the up or down arrows shown left of the comment
        author.
        
        
        Dependencies
        ============
        
        This product works only with plone.app.discussion, which as of Plone 4.1 is the default commenting
        framework for Plone. 
        
        
        Changelog
        =========
        
        0.1a2 (2012-03-02)
        ------------------
        
        - Fixed compatibility with plone.app.discussion 2.3.1 [jcbrand] 
        
        
        0.1a1 (2011-03-24)
        ------------------
        
        - Initial release
        
